Instructions to note before execution

1) This assignment is developed requires java using Spring Boot framework. So a runtime for java with version 8 is required.

2) Open the project in an java supported tool and execute the main file.

3) Endpoints for add/update/get payment methods are listed in controller layer. Additionally swagger can be integrated for assistance

4) H2 in memory db is used that creates required tables and insert some initial data into it. You are not required to make any other configurations
